reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars It's cheap and works.
reviews.reviewText: Not revolutionary of course, the case weighs next to nothing and is not the most sturdy shell case you can buy. But for the purpose of storing and protecting a PSP in a drawer can't ask for anything better. The interior straps will hold the PSP firmly and the clip it comes with is a nice addition.
